cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SI 

This paper deals with improving the precision of feedforward neural networks, which is a topic closely related to neural network optimization and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses the use of cost functions and optimization techniques, which are common topics in machine learning and deep learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also presents examples of function approximation and image compression, which are related to computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper proposes an efficient GPU version of the algorithm, which is related to scientific computing (cs.SI).
